data.title: Calling all professional artists across disciplines to apply for a 3-week international residency in France in 2024. 2 Awards available...
data.meta_description:
72 likes, 2 comments - ateliersamuelbeckett11 on February 1, 2024: "Calling all professional artists across disciplines to apply for a 3-week international residency in France in 2024. 

2 Awards available in this round. 

Ireland Eyes Bursary and the D.Kern & Elizabeth R. Holoman Bursary.

Apply by 14th February 2024, 6pm (Irish Time). 

Link to apply in bio!

Follow us and stay up to date on upcoming events and bursaries!".
